        "summary": "Retrieve trust reconciliation statement dates and corresponding trust reconciliation history guids for given date range.",
        "description": "*Utilise [GET /api/v1/reporting/getasyncrequest/{requestId}](https://leap.build/api-reference/#tag/Reporting/paths/~1api~1v1~1reporting~1getasyncrequest~1%7Brequestid%7D/get) to retrieve results.*\n",
