            "description": "LEAP GUID of the Card record for the Purchase Supplier. Card records for a firm can be retrieved from [GET /api/v2/cards](http://leap.build/api-reference/#tag/Cards/operation/Card_GetCards) or [GET /api/v1/cards/search](http://leap.build/api-reference/#tag/Cards/paths/~1api~1v1~1cards~1search/get).",
            "format": "uuid"
          },
          "WarningAcknowledgments": {
            "type": "array",
            "description": "These are typical CostRecovery warnings, which would prevent any CostRecovery from being created. Add these items, if you wish to ignore these warnings and allow the creation to continue. \n\nExamples: \n\n\t1001 (Matter has exceeded the estimate of matterDisbursementsEstimate) \n\n\t1099 (This matter is archived)",
